These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: garlic, artichoke, peas, cranberry, blueberry, cauliflower, strawberry
There are 7 different nationalities: polish, chinese, indian, egyptian, dutch, nigerian, indonesian
 1. the person eating peas is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating cranberry is not the nigerian##6
 3. the polish is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
 5. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
 6. the polish is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 7. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere between the person eating artichoke and the chinese##7
 8. the chinese is on the left of the indonesian##1
 9. the egyptian is somewhere between the person eating blueberry and the indian##7
10. the indian is on the left or right of the polish##3
11. the dutch is on the far left##1
12. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the left of the indonesian##5
13. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating cauliflower##5
14. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating blueberry##5
15. the person eating blueberry is the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | peas    | garlic    | artichoke | cauliflower | cranberry | blueberry    | strawberry |
| Nationality   | dutch | polish | indian  | nigerian   | egyptian    | chinese | indonesian |

