.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: orange, apple, cauliflower, peas, asparagus, peach, watermelon
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, cooking, video-games, photography, puzzles, filmmaking, traveling
 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere between the person eating watermelon and the person eating apple##7
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person eating peas##1
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person eating orange is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 6. the person eating peach is somewhere between the person eating peas and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
 7. the person eating asparagus is somewhere between the person eating peas and the person eating apple##7
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the person eating asparagus##5
10. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not the person eating watermelon##6
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person eating peas##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | watermelon  | cauliflower | peach | peas | orange     | asparagus | apple  |
| Hobby   | video-games | filmmaking | cooking  | traveling  | puzzles | photography      | woodworking |

