 3. the fan of punk is not the person who's hobby is puzzles##6
 4. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the fan of funk##5
 5. the fan of trance is between the fan of funk and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
 6. the fan of folk is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
 9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere between the fan of indie and the fan of classical##7
10. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the fan of trance##6
13. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
14. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
15. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
16. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the fan of funk##6
17. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
18. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
